      "uuid": "875dc6f3-68f7-42a6-9660-9cc336c73742",
      "text": " Looking at the insurance changes for your 2017 Toyota Camry (VIN: 4T1BF1FK8HU781128), here are the key changes between your previous and new coverage:\n\n1. Rental Reimbursement:\n- Previous: $40 per day at $36.01/6 months\n- New: Opted out ($0.00/6 months)\n\n2. Comprehensive Coverage:\n- Previous: $500 deductible at $152.75/6 months\n- New: Opted out ($0.00/6 months)\n\n3. Collision Deductible Waiver:\n- Previous: Yes\n- New: No\n- Cost: See revised premium\n\n4. Collision Coverage:\n- Previous: $1,000 deductible at $495.56/6 months\n- New: Opted out ($0.00/6 months)\n\n5. Uninsured/Underinsured Motorist:\n- Previous: $30K per person / $60K per accident at $308.45/6 months\n- New: $15K per person / $30K per accident at $246.76/6 months\n\nOverall, it appears you've reduced coverage levels and opted out of several coverages, which has resulted in lower premiums across these categories.",
