      "text": " Let me add this property damage coverage change to the previous list:\n\n6. Property Damage:\n- Previous: $100K per accident at $195.40/6 months\n- New: $10K per accident at $189.82/6 months\n- Note: This applies to all vehicles\n\nThis represents a significant reduction in property damage liability coverage, dropping from $100,000 to $10,000 per accident, with a small decrease in premium of about $5.58 per 6-month period.\n\nWould you like me to analyze the total premium changes across all these coverage modifications?",
