      "uuid": "f6a1f8c1-0016-414d-bc7e-77a4f3a6b198",
      "text": " Subject: Summary of Car Insurance Changes - 2017 Toyota Camry\n\nDear Lucia,\n\nHere are the recent changes made to my car insurance coverage:\n\nAll coverages have been reduced or removed:\n- Rental reimbursement: Removed (was $40/day)\n- Comprehensive: Removed (was $500 deductible)\n- Collision: Removed (was $1,000 deductible)\n- Collision deductible waiver: Removed\n- Uninsured motorist: Reduced from $30K/$60K to $15K/$30K\n- Property damage: Reduced from $100K to $10K per accident\n\nTotal 6-month savings across these changes: About $761 ($152.75 + $495.56 + $61.69 + $5.58 + $36.01)\n\nPlease let me know if you need any additional details.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your name]",
